data.description: CASH INCENTIVE - Seller to contribute $5,000 towards buyer's closing costs with an acceptable offer. // A perfect home for a growing family with a generational family need! A 4th bedroom & 3rd bath are downstairs for an aging parent or that teenager that wants their own space! Upstairs, 2 other bedrooms and a large Master bedroom that features an attached office, den, nursery, workout room, sitting area (a true Flex room). If you're looking for LOW utility bills, the solar system is OWNED & FULLY PAID FOR & the Trane AC units are new as of 2019 & 2023! Want security? A SMART security system included! Want storage? 3 car epoxied floor garage w/ storage rack & storage shed. Eat in island kitchen, maple cabinets, granite counters, GAS cooktop - A low maintenance backyard is artificially turfed, has a natural gas firepit & a Hot Tub ! Lots of square footage for the $$ ! Sellers can close quick!
